::Killfest/Incarcinator::

Killfest nods, entering the scanning room. Scyther was no where to be seen, but Killfest walks over to a chair.

"Scyther, uncloak. We need to talk to you," he says, an outline of a bot shimmering into view and then Scyther appearing, sitting on the chair. He turns toward the group of commanders.

"What do you need?" he asks them.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Incarcinator gets his drink, walking over to KitKat and StarScream like that uncivil encounter had never happened.

"That was an interesting battle last battle, wasn't it?"
